      <title>波兰总统图斯克称俄罗斯策划针对航空公司的恐怖行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/poland-s-tusk-says-russia-planned-terror-acts-against-airlines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰总理唐纳德·塔斯克指责俄罗斯策划对全球航空公司实施“空中恐怖行为”，并敦促欧洲伙伴联合起来抵制莫斯科所谓的破坏企图。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/poland-s-tusk-says-russia-planned-terror-acts-against-airlines</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 16:21:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登政府在离任前加强对俄罗斯的制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/biden-administration-hardens-russia-sanctions-before-departing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府于周三采取行动，加大了当选总统唐纳德·特朗普解除对俄罗斯部分制裁的难度，这是在新团队上任前几天做出的告别发言。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/biden-administration-hardens-russia-sanctions-before-departing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 15:33:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>邦迪誓言司法部在她的领导下不会有“敌人名单”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/bondi-pledges-one-tier-of-justice-as-attorney-general</link>
      <description><![CDATA[候任总统唐纳德·特朗普挑选的司法部长候选人表示，如果她得到确认，司法部将不会有“敌人名单”，这与保守派的观点形成了鲜明对比，保守派希望司法部调查和起诉那些反对或调查特朗普及其盟友的人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/bondi-pledges-one-tier-of-justice-as-attorney-general</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 15:21:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢比奥在美国高级外交官听证会上面对友好同事</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/rubio-to-face-friendly-colleagues-as-trump-hearings-continue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议院外交关系委员会的共和党和民主党高层在佛罗里达州参议员马尔科·卢比奥的国务卿提名听证会上共同赞扬了这位参议员，这意味着卢比奥将面临当选总统唐纳德·特朗普内阁中最容易的确认之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/rubio-to-face-friendly-colleagues-as-trump-hearings-continue</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 15:10:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国与毛里求斯即将达成的查戈斯协议指南</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/chagos-islands-what-will-uk-mauritius-deal-mean-for-diego-garcia-military-base</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国对查戈斯群岛超过两个世纪的统治即将结束，英国准备将印度洋群岛的所有权移交给毛里求斯。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/chagos-islands-what-will-uk-mauritius-deal-mean-for-diego-garcia-military-base</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 14:47:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国总理愿意通过新养老金法以争取支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/french-premier-open-to-new-pension-law-in-bid-for-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总理弗朗索瓦·贝鲁承诺将养老金法修改提案提交议会，即便所有党派不同意修改内容，目的是满足社会党人的一项关键要求，获得他们的默许支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/french-premier-open-to-new-pension-law-in-bid-for-support</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 14:42:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京将要求乌克兰在任何特朗普会谈中永远不要加入北约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/putin-trump-talks-would-see-russia-demand-ukraine-cut-back-nato-ties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，在与美国新任总统唐纳德·特朗普的任何会谈中，俄罗斯将要求乌克兰大幅削减与北约联盟的军事联系，并成为一个拥有有限军队的中立国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/putin-trump-talks-would-see-russia-demand-ukraine-cut-back-nato-ties</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 14:24:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士国防部长因军事问题遭批评而辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/swiss-federal-councilor-viola-amherd-announces-resignation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在瑞士军队采购项目受到批评的背景下，瑞士国防部长维奥拉·阿姆赫德宣布辞职，这一举动令人意外。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/swiss-federal-councilor-viola-amherd-announces-resignation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 13:39:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普交通部长提名人称波音需要“严厉管控”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/trump-s-transport-pick-vows-to-cut-red-tape-prioritize-safety</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普选择领导美国运输部，誓言确保波音公司实施一项计划，以加强其安全和制造实践，如果确认担任该职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/trump-s-transport-pick-vows-to-cut-red-tape-prioritize-safety</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克在争议投票的阴影下举行新总统就职典礼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/mozambique-to-inaugurate-president-in-shadow-of-disputed-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹尼尔·查波于周三宣誓就任莫桑比克新总统，他接任的国家领导人因数月的抗议活动而支离破碎，抗议活动夺去了数百人的生命，使国家经济陷入瘫痪 — — 而且很多人不认为他是合法当选的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/mozambique-to-inaugurate-president-in-shadow-of-disputed-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
